openmediavault-clamav (4.1.13-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Issue #607: Error using on-access scanner.
  * Set ReceiveTimeout=300 (5 minutes) in freshclam.conf,
    otherwise the database download will never succeed
    because it will be restarted every 30 seconds when
    the download was not successful during that time.

